WITH DiagnosedPatients AS (
    SELECT p.subject_id
    FROM patients p
    INNER JOIN diagnoses_icd d ON p.subject_id = d.subject_id
    INNER JOIN d_icd_diagnoses ddi ON d.icd_code = ddi.icd_code
    WHERE ddi.long_title LIKE '%Other psychotic disorder%' AND ddi.long_title NOT LIKE '%Substance%' AND ddi.long_title NOT LIKE '%Known physiological condition%'
),
TreatedPatients AS (
    SELECT DISTINCT p.subject_id
    FROM DiagnosedPatients p
    INNER JOIN prescriptions pr ON p.subject_id = pr.subject_id
    WHERE pr.drug LIKE '%Alteplase%'
)
SELECT 
    CAST(SUM(CASE WHEN julianday(p.dod) - julianday(p.dob) <= 90 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS REAL) * 100 / COUNT(*) AS survival_rate
FROM patients p
WHERE p.subject_id IN (SELECT subject_id FROM TreatedPatients)

WITH PatientSurvival AS (
    SELECT 
        p.subject_id,
        p.gender,
        p.dob,
        p.dod,
        a.admittime,
        a.dischtime,
        d.long_title AS diagnosis,
        pr.drug AS prescribed_drug,
        pr.stoptime AS drug_stop_time
    FROM patients p
    INNER JOIN admissions a ON p.subject_id = a.subject_id
    INNER JOIN diagnoses_icd di ON a.hadm_id = di.hadm_id
    INNER JOIN d_icd_diagnoses d ON di.icd_code = d.icd_code
    INNER JOIN prescriptions pr ON a.hadm_id = pr.hadm_id
    WHERE d.long_title LIKE '%unspecified atrial fibrillation%'

WITH RecentAdmissions AS (
    SELECT 
        a.subject_id,
        a.hadm_id,
        a.admittime,
        d.icd_code
    FROM admissions a
    JOIN diagnoses_icd d ON a.hadm_id = d.hadm_id
    WHERE a.admittime >= date('now', '-1 year') 
),
FilteredPatients AS (
    SELECT 
        p.subject_id
    FROM patients p
    JOIN RecentAdmissions ra ON p.subject_id = ra.subject_id
    WHERE p.gender IN ('M', 'F') AND p.dob <= date('now', '-40 years')
),
FrequentDiagnoses AS (
    SELECT 
        ra.icd_code,
        COUNT(*) AS diagnosis_count
    FROM RecentAdmissions ra
    JOIN FilteredPatients fp ON ra.subject_id = fp.subject_id
    GROUP BY ra.icd_code
)
SELECT 
    d.long_title,
    fd.diagnosis_count
FROM FrequentDiagnoses fd
JOIN d_icd_diagnoses d ON fd.icd_code = d.icd_code
ORDER BY fd.diagnosis_count DESC
LIMIT 3;
